snippet.title: Dark and Darker - Official Alpha Playtest Teaser
snippet.description:
Take a look at Dark and Darker, an upcoming unforgiving hardcore fantasy FPS dungeon PvPvE adventure. 

In Dark and Darker, band together with your friends and use your courage, wits, and cunning to uncover mythical treasures, and defeat gruesome monsters, while staying one step ahead of the other devious treasure hunters.
